cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.CC, cs.FL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the Logic of Repeating Values and its connection to games.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the generation of multi-attributed data words.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of valuations for variables.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper proves undecidability results.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses games played on infinite alphabets.
